decision_conditions:
Condition : 7 - The illuminated advertisement hereby approved shall comply with the following terms:
	
(a)	The intensity of the illumination of the advertisement shall not exceed 100 cd/m2;
(b)	The advertisement shall be fitted with a light intensity monitoring censor to ensure the illuminance intensity is dimmable to take account of ambient light conditions and comply with the maximum recommended lighting intensity; 
(c)	The advertisement shall not display any moving, or apparently moving, images; 

Reason: In the interests of amenity and highway safety.
